Ransom et al., Respondents, v. Masten, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. May 27, 1889.) For opinion on appeal, see 4 N. Y. Supp. 781.

Argued before Landon and Ingalls, JJ.

No opinion. Motion for reargument or to go to court of appeals denied, with $10 costs.
